1. *Matirao* je protivnika u samo nekoliko poteza. (He checkmated his opponent in just a few moves.)
2. Njegova majka mu je *mati*. (His mother is his mother.)
3. On je *matičar* u lokalnoj opštini. (He is a registrar at the local municipality.)
4. *Materijal* za ovaj projekat je već nabavljen. (The material for this project has already been procured.)
5. Nemoj da me *maltretiraš* svaki dan. (Don't harass me every day.)
6. Ona je *matrijarhalna* figura u porodici. (She is a matriarchal figure in the family.)
7. Tkanina na ovom kauču je mekana i *matirana*. (The fabric on this couch is soft and matte.)
8. *Maticu* za ovaj uređaj možete pronaći u prodavnici elektronskih komponenti. (You can find the circuit board for this device at an electronics components store.)
9. Moramo imati jasan *matematički* pristup ovom problemu. (We need to have a clear mathematical approach to this problem.)
10. Oni su *matični* preduzetnici i zapošljavaju više od 50 radnika. (They are founding entrepreneurs and employ more than 50 workers.)